    "catalogs": [],
    "contents": "<p>添加<code>overlay</code>属性，即可展示带遮罩层的加载动画，此时包含<code>Spin</code>的容器必须是定位元素，动画元素默认会居中展示，所以<code>center</code>属性在该情况下无效</p>\n",
    "index": 63,
    "highlighted": [
        {
            "language": "vdt",
            "content": "<pre><code class=\"hljs jsx\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> Spin <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'kpc/components/spin'</span>;\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> {Table, TableColumn} <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'kpc/components/table'</span>;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> data = [\n    {<span class=\"hljs-attr\">a</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'第一行'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">b</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'哈哈2'</span>}, \n    {<span class=\"hljs-attr\">a</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'第二行'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">b</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'哈哈2'</span>},\n    {<span class=\"hljs-attr\">a</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'第三行'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">b</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'哈哈3'</span>},\n];\n\n&lt;div class=\"wrapper\"&gt;\n    &lt;Table data={{ data }}&gt;\n        &lt;TableColumn key=\"a\" title=\"表头1\" /&gt;\n        &lt;TableColumn key=\"b\" title=\"表头2\" /&gt;\n    &lt;/Table&gt;\n    &lt;Spin overlay /&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>"
        },
